FFXIV Venues Directory (Plugin Project)

This folder is the actual Dalamud plugin project.

If you just want user-facing docs, start from the repository root:
../README.md

What this project contains:
- In-game browser for approved FFXIV Venues listings.
- Search/filter/sort UI with venue details, schedules, tags, and banner preview.
- Local preference state (favorite / visited).
- Optional visit integration button that is shown only when a compatible third-party plugin is installed and enabled.

Command:
- /ffxivvenues

Build from repo root:
- dotnet build FFXIV.Venues.Directory.sln -c Release -p:Platform=x64
